               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18470510-name-113" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18470510-name-113" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470510-name-113" type="surname" value="PERRY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470510-name-113" type="given" value="MARIA"></interp>MARIA PERRY</persName>
                  </hi>. I live with my brother, Samuel Robert Perry. On the 8th of April, between three and four o'clock, the prisoners came to the shop for a halfpenny—worth of plums—directly they were gone I missed a weight which I had seen safe five minutes before—I ran out, calling, "Stop, thief!"—I saw them both running away together—they were brought back by a policeman—these are the weights—they are my brother's—I picked up one of them, which was dropped in the road.</p>
